    ViewBag.Title = "Home";
}

<div class="jumbotron">
    <h3><b>Information Systems - Brigham Young University</b></h3>
    <div class="banner"><img src="http://www.ccny.cuny.edu/is/images/infobanner.jpg" /></div>
    <p>Everyone likes to have career options. Few programs will give you more than a degree in Information Systems</p>
    <ul>
        <li>Study in two worlds - business and technology - and learn to help them work together. Learn how to desing, develop, implement, manage, and advise on information technology systems and processes.</li>
